00:33:59,180 --> 00:34:06,788
♫  Before bidding farewell, we expect an encounter  ♫

464
00:34:08,339 --> 00:34:10,479
 - Changge, it's a trap. 
 - Sun? 

465
00:34:10,479 --> 00:34:12,840
 Your friends were caught. 

466
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:15,100
 I followed the man that wanted to catch you. 

467
00:34:15,100 --> 00:34:16,738
 I didn't imagine you were really here. 

468
00:34:16,738 --> 00:34:18,239
 Then, Yueyan... 

469
00:34:18,239 --> 00:34:19,738
 There're imperial officers. 

470
00:34:19,738 --> 00:34:22,539
 Relax, she's safe. Just leave here. 

471
00:34:23,399 --> 00:34:25,220
 You don't hate me? 

