00:34:48,879 --> 00:34:54,759
♫  It turns into an eternity. The cocoon in the dark night  ♫

479
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:55,899
What's this place?

480
00:34:55,899 --> 00:34:57,438
The most famous tavern in Luoyang.

481
00:34:57,438 --> 00:35:01,059
They won't believe that we'd be hiding in the most crowded place.

482
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:06,058
How could you be so familiar with this place?

483
00:35:06,058 --> 00:35:08,300
I played chess here with a friend.

484
00:35:08,300 --> 00:35:10,500
Played chess here?

485
00:35:24,339 --> 00:35:28,839
Changge, it was so difficult for me...

486
00:35:30,950 --> 00:35:32,750
to find you.

487
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:47,159
You've been looking for me from the tribes until now?

488
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,680
I'm the one who let you down.

489
00:35:57,959 --> 00:35:59,899
I shouldn't have blamed you.

490
00:36:01,639 --> 00:36:03,719
I owe you so much.

491
00:36:03,719 --> 00:36:05,580
Then don't leave.

492
00:36:06,520 --> 00:36:08,239
You can pay it back slowly.

493
00:36:17,979 --> 00:36:19,739
I just saved you.

494
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:22,439
Shouldn't you give me a toast?

495
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:26,320
Thank you so much for saving me.

496
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:34,618
I just want to thank you.

497
00:36:34,618 --> 00:36:36,680
I didn't say I would marry you.

498
00:36:37,259 --> 00:36:39,120
Who'll benefit more,

499
00:36:40,299 --> 00:36:41,979
we still don't know yet.

500
00:37:02,919 --> 00:37:04,999
Sister?

501
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,958
I just heard your voice.

502
00:37:06,959 --> 00:37:10,460
I didn't believe it was you.

503
00:37:11,180 --> 00:37:13,279
Ghost. You're a ghost!

504
00:37:13,279 --> 00:37:15,678
Shut up. Why are you here?

505
00:37:15,678 --> 00:37:18,400
Don't you know you've caused big trouble?

506
00:37:26,040 --> 00:37:30,140
Sister, you're alive.

507
00:37:31,499 --> 00:37:33,139
Congratulations.

508
00:37:33,139 --> 00:37:35,540
- Long time no— 
 - Answer my question!

509
00:37:35,540 --> 00:37:38,638
I... I sneaked out.

510
00:37:38,638 --> 00:37:41,538
It's said this tavern is interesting.

511
00:37:41,538 --> 00:37:45,099
Western dancers with golden hair and blue eyes will dance here.

512
00:37:47,620 --> 00:37:50,679
So I was thinking... I...

513
00:37:50,679 --> 00:37:53,679
So, you sneaked out.

514
00:37:53,679 --> 00:37:55,500
You weren't kidnapped.

515
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:59,820
Boy, think clearly.

516
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:01,740
Have you been staying here?

517
00:38:02,579 --> 00:38:04,398
Do you know there was a fire at Ziwei Palace?

518
00:38:04,399 --> 00:38:06,638
I... I heard about it.

519
00:38:06,638 --> 00:38:08,258
But why didn't you go back?

520
00:38:08,258 --> 00:38:09,538
I...

521
00:38:09,538 --> 00:38:12,678
When the fire broke out, I'd fallen asleep.

522
00:38:12,678 --> 00:38:14,198
I heard about it later.

523
00:38:14,199 --> 00:38:16,579
If I go back now,

524
00:38:16,579 --> 00:38:18,438
Minister Du will punish me.

525
00:38:18,439 --> 00:38:19,839
You naughty boy.

526
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:22,419
Li Changge! I'm the crown prince now.

527
00:38:22,419 --> 00:38:23,718
How could you do this to me?

528
00:38:23,719 --> 00:38:25,539
I'll hit you if you keep talking.

529
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,979
Li Changge, if you dare to touch me one more time...

