00:38:28,979 --> 00:38:31,119
Sister! Sister!

531
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:34,379
I'm your brother. Just calm down.

532
00:38:34,379 --> 00:38:35,500
I won't say that to you.

533
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:37,699
Li Chengqian, even a three-year-old can see through you.

534
00:38:37,699 --> 00:38:39,429
You really haven't gotten any better as you have gotten older.

535
00:38:39,429 --> 00:38:41,578
You're a crown prince, but you did such a ridiculous thing.

536
00:38:41,578 --> 00:38:43,119
I feel ashamed for Li Shimin.

537
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:44,958
How could he have a son like you?

538
00:38:44,959 --> 00:38:46,499
You didn't learn a little from your father.

539
00:38:46,499 --> 00:38:47,818
You want to be a crown prince?

